{"tid":83834,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"有人同我講 九西紫禁城同高鐵 係一個風水陣","createTime":"2017-01-17T05:20:32.000Z","updateTime":"2017-01-18T01:04:47.000Z","uid":13663,"like":4,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"304c8ccc0ec8f2bf6e0cc61c5f6bcdd0f26f0aee","tid":83834,"uid":13663,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-17T05:20:32.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/32.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />支共續命風水陣<br />\n借香港大運<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/24.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6515658ec340628f33c8ac4ee6116f61269f4b09","tid":83834,"uid":13663,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-17T05:22:53.000Z","msg":"嚴x奇表面上係建築師<br />\n但實際上係風水師<br />\n689間屋都係搵佢搞..."},{"pid":"b9426d23b461f98c6f2b2f8b2879af9cc190c88c","tid":83834,"uid":72713,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-17T05:22:57.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/32.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />支共續命風水陣<br />\n借香港大運<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/24.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"710e538394387e4235a44657d43368d93389c96e","tid":83834,"uid":13663,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-17T05:25:30.000Z","msg":"林忌：梁振英與嚴迅奇的不解關係｜特約轉載<br />\n&nbsp;2017-1-10 16:59<br />\n<br />\n字體：&nbsp;A&nbsp;A&nbsp;A<br />\n<br />\n1992年裕熙園落成，建築師係嚴迅奇<br />\n<br />\n1999年梁振英買樓，賴上手業主冇畀圖則，合約卻見到嚴迅奇簽名的圖則<br />\n<br />\n2001年梁振英多次申請改建大宅，代梁申請的建築師就係嚴迅奇（見此文件）；而作為此樓的原設計人，嚴迅奇竟然看不見樓內的僭建物<br />\n<br />\n2002年西九比賽嚴迅奇團體得優異獎，梁振英就係冇利益申報的評判<br />\n<br />\n2011年5月15日明報報導梁振英以大宅招待記者，自稱大宅由嚴迅奇設計，絕冇僭建<br />\n<br />\n2011 年 9 月 24 日西九管理局公開最終的西九文化區概念圖則，偏要加入使用早前落選的嚴迅奇設計<br />\n<br />\n2012年11月23日梁振英解釋僭建的聲明附件中，遮掩保護嚴迅奇的簽名（見此文件及之後的一頁）<br />\n<br />\n2016年6月起，嚴迅奇秘密獲聘開展故宮博物館的設計工作，以代號 Project P 進行（傳真社消息）<br />\n<br />\n2016年11月28日西九董事局才通過博物館計劃，同時委任嚴迅奇負責設計。換言之，嚴迅奇在董事局通過聘任前5個月，甚至未獲馬會資金之前，已偷步獲得委任。<br />\n<br />\n（圖片來源：蘋果日報）"},{"pid":"55bc0dd77c4bcc0c5296f761e36ad86ecbd7f172","tid":83834,"uid":20816,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-17T05:26:33.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5efd10dac5ca1ed57eb4afcd713171e2ef693c95","tid":83834,"uid":42044,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-17T05:26:54.000Z","msg":"借左係要還，所以大陸一死會勁慘。"},{"pid":"668f616a43adc45e2a62753c6d4c15d4fda5c892","tid":83834,"uid":13663,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-17T05:27:34.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://assets.post852.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/01/10161931/image1484036360234.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fassets.post852.com%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2017%2F01%2F10161931%2Fimage1484036360234.png&h=376aa319&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"9d0984a37217bb92ca9f7767e31a2d5da532634b","tid":83834,"uid":13663,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-17T05:28:11.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>借左係要還，所以大陸一死會勁慘。</blockquote><br />\n同689一樣<br />\n根本冇運做特首<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/13.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e042c08d137795eb9f50195f6bdd98ed9b1edcb1","tid":83834,"uid":76310,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-17T05:29:32.000Z","msg":"所以支爆必先港爆，香港已經做左強國替死鬼<br />\n<br />\n先死替身，才到正身"},{"pid":"f73abcf4b5472c7a9306dee57a57cee8f5736ad8","tid":83834,"uid":76310,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-17T05:37:26.000Z","msg":"個風水陣<br />\n如果從地圖來看，高鐵好似一支吸血管直香港心臟，比強國吸血為強國續命<br />\n<br />\n所以支爆前必先港爆"},{"pid":"20552e2aad6beb9a2e69f2341fc4da8b0df5d990","tid":83834,"uid":20816,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-17T05:42:33.000Z","msg":"呢條龍係咪都係風水陣？<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/a/ab/HK_Wan_Chai_Morrison_Hill_Road_n_Tin_Lok_Lane.JPG\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fupload.wikimedia.org%2Fwikipedia%2Fcommons%2Fa%2Fab%2FHK_Wan_Chai_Morrison_Hill_Road_n_Tin_Lok_Lane.JPG&h=574dc997&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"4ecca42321f1d11a77dfeb7d8613b39175b926a8","tid":83834,"uid":22858,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-17T05:57:52.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>呢條龍係咪都係風水陣？<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/a/ab/HK_Wan_Chai_Morrison_Hill_Road_n_Tin_Lok_Lane.JPG\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fupload.wikimedia.org%2Fwikipedia%2Fcommons%2Fa%2Fab%2FHK_Wan_Chai_Morrison_Hill_Road_n_Tin_Lok_Lane.JPG&h=574dc997&s={SIZE}\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n深井隻鵝 <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5266580c6db52ff52acc6945e04636ac4ce78a91","tid":83834,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-17T06:12:47.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9d9b7f30542f9ec0aa6451ad3bba2fec8592ef06","tid":83834,"uid":34005,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-17T06:13:08.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>個風水陣<br />\n如果從地圖來看，高鐵好似一支吸血管直香港心臟，比強國吸血為強國續命<br />\n<br />\n所以支爆前必先港爆</blockquote><br />\n屌 咁講法同慈禧話起鐵路破壞風水有咩分別<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e6b637f94a81cdfd18e08aac4ea84ad31be7252f","tid":83834,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-17T06:15:28.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/10841/page/1\" target=\"_bla