解釋僭建的聲明附件中，遮掩保護嚴迅奇的簽名（見此文件及之後的一頁）<br />\n<br />\n2016年6月起，嚴迅奇秘密獲聘開展故宮博物館的設計工作，以代號 Project P 進行（傳真社消息）<br />\n<br />\n2016年11月28日西九董事局才通過博物館計劃，同時委任嚴迅奇負責設計。換言之，嚴迅奇在董事局通過聘任前5個月，甚至未獲馬會資金之前，已偷步獲得委任。<br />\n<br />\n（圖片來源：蘋果日報）</blockquote><br />\n唔怪得西九單野奶晒閪咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d6fcde6c5f2f51e3cfebbd92f6bb33098772fb87","tid":83834,"uid":3659,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-17T07:36:15.000Z","msg":"點解陣<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n連登仔集思廣益下"},{"pid":"5f29b04893988eb110ef167270a8a5df67ca5f2a","tid":83834,"uid":20816,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-17T09:25:39.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>點解陣<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n連登仔集思廣益下</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n宣布孫中山係恐佈份子"},{"pid":"948c3f5c8034e213d3dba8dd1a7a95cd36b94ae6","tid":83834,"uid":13663,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-17T11:12:55.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/40.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f26b4f3ab27cae9ea2657679c8088e2c1eceae29","tid":83834,"uid":60615,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-17T11:18:27.000Z","msg":"雙氧教話西九係共濟會核心黎架"},{"pid":"85d50334fb5a262a23ab33ad391ad8c9b8884107","tid":83834,"uid":53186,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-17T17:47:30.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><img src=\"http://scontent.xx.fbcdn.net/v/t1.0-9/s720x720/10384596_10152452057212844_8526156441858897833_n.jpg?oh=16146047ea8a08beda3a83d0a951051f&amp;oe=58C873AD\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fscontent.xx.fbcdn.net%2Fv%2Ft1.0-9%2Fs720x720%2F10384596_10152452057212844_8526156441858897833_n.jpg%3Foh%3D16146047ea8a08beda3a83d0a951051f%26oe%3D58C873AD&h=47129910&s={SIZE}\" /></blockquote><br />\n死光<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"822adc1e8ec4f3c4c96feb2989b65efe04072748